<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>MobilePay payments | Stripe Documentation</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Learn how to accept MobilePay, a popular payment method in Denmark and Finland.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="layout">
    <nav class="nav">
      <div class="nav-container">
        <div class="nav-brand">
          <span class="nav-logo">Stripe</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="nav-menu">
          <li><a href="/" class="nav-link">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="/billing/subscriptions/coupons" class="nav-link">Coupons</a></li>
          <li><a href="/capital/marketing" class="nav-link">Marketing</a></li>
          <li><a href="/payments/mobilepay/accept-a-payment" class="nav-link active">Accept A Payment</a></li>
          <li><a href="/payments" class="nav-link">Payments</a></li>
          <li><a href="/upgrades" class="nav-link">Upgrades</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="main">
      <div class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/" class="breadcrumb-link">Documentation</a>
        <span class="breadcrumb-separator">/</span>
        <a href="/payments" class="breadcrumb-link">Payments</a>
        <span class="breadcrumb-separator">/</span>
        <span class="breadcrumb-current">MobilePay</span>
      </div>

      <div class="hero">
        <h1 class="hero-title">MobilePay payments</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">Learn how to accept MobilePay, a popular payment method in Denmark and Finland.</p>
        
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <button class="btn">Ask about this page</button>
          <button class="btn btn-secondary">Copy for LLM</button>
          <button class="btn btn-secondary">View as Markdown</button>
        </div>

        <div class="integration-tabs">
          <button class="tab-btn active">Web</button>
          <button class="tab-btn">Mobile</button>
          <button class="tab-btn">Stripe-hosted page</button>
          <button class="tab-btn">Advanced integration</button>
          <button class="tab-btn">Direct API</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <div class="intro-card">
          <p>MobilePay is a <a href="https://docs.stripe.com/payments/payment-methods#usage" class="inline-link">single-use</a> card payment method popular in Denmark and Finland. It allows customers to pay using their mobile phones through the MobilePay app.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556742049-0cfed4f6a45d?w=24&h=24&fit=crop" alt="Failed payments" class="card-icon">
              <h2 class="card-title">Failed payments</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card-content">
              <p>MobilePay transactions can fail if the underlying card transaction is declined. Learn more about <a href="https://docs.stripe.com/declines/card" class="inline-link">card declines</a>. In this case, the PaymentMethod is detached and cannot be reused.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?w=24&h=24&fit=crop" alt="Refunds and disputes" class="card-icon">
              <h2 class="card-title">Refunds and disputes</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card-content">
              <p>Stripe performs a card transaction using standard card rails as part of a MobilePay transaction. <a href="https://docs.stripe.com/refunds" class="inline-link">Refunds</a> and <a href="https://docs.stripe.com/disputes/how-disputes" class="inline-link">disputes</a> work the same way as regular card payments.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-section">
          <h2 class="section-title">Integration steps</h2>
          <div class="step-list">
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-number">1</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3 class="step-title">Enable MobilePay</h3>
                <p class="step-description">Enable MobilePay in your Stripe Dashboard under Payment Methods.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-number">2</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3 class="step-title">Create Payment Intent</h3>
                <p class="step-description">Create a PaymentIntent with MobilePay as an available payment method.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-number">3</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3 class="step-title">Handle authentication</h3>
                <p class="step-description">Direct customers to the MobilePay app for payment confirmation.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="see-also">
          <div class="card-header">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517077304055-6e89abbf09b0?w=24&h=24&fit=crop" alt="See also" class="card-icon">
            <h2 class="card-title">See also</h2>
          </div>
          <ul class="see-also-list">
            <li><a href="https://docs.stripe.com/payments/mobilepay" class="inline-link">More about MobilePay</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://docs.stripe.com/checkout/fulfillment" class="inline-link">Checkout fulfillment</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://docs.stripe.com/payments/checkout" class="inline-link">Customize Checkout</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>

  <style>
    :root {
      --brand: #635BFF;
      --brand-alt: #0A2540;
      --bg: #FFFFFF;
      --surface: #F7F9FA;
      --text: #0A2540;
      --muted: #6B7280;
      
      --font-heading: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      --font-body: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      
      --space-0: 0px;
      --space-1: 4px;
      --space-2: 8px;
      --space-3: 12px;
      --space-4: 16px;
      --space-5: 20px;
      --space-6: 24px;
      --space-7: 28px;
      --space-8: 32px;
      --space-10: 40px;
      --space-12: 48px;
      --space-16: 64px;
      --space-20: 80px;
      
      --radius-sm: 6px;
      --radius-md: 8px;
      --radius-lg: 12px;
      
      --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      --shadow-md: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      color: var(--text);
      background-color: var(--bg);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .layout {
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .nav {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--surface);
      background: var(--bg);
    }

    .nav-container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-6);
    }

    .nav-logo {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: var(--brand);
    }

    .nav-menu {
      display: flex;
      list-style: none;
      gap: var(--space-6);
    }

    .nav-link {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .nav-link:hover,
    .nav-link.active {
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .main {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: var(--space-6);
    }

    .breadcrumb {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--space-2);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }

    .breadcrumb-link {
      color: var(--brand);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .breadcrumb-separator {
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .breadcrumb-current {
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .hero {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: var(--space-3);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .integration-tabs {
      display: flex;
      gap: var(--space-1);
      background: var(--surface);
      padding: var(--space-1);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .tab-btn {
      padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-4);
      background: transparent;
      border: none;
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }

    .tab-btn.active {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }

    .tab-btn:hover {
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .intro-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      padding: var(--space-6);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
    }

    .inline-link {
      color: var(--brand);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
    }

    .inline-link:hover {
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--space-6);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--surface);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: var(--space-6);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
      transition: box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    }

    .card-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--space-3);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }

    .card-icon {
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    }

    .card-title {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .card-content {
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .feature-section {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
    }

    .section-title {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    }

    .step-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-6);
    }

    .step {
      display: flex;
      gap: var(--space-4);
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .step-number {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      background: var(--brand);
      color: var(--bg);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .step-title {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    }

    .step-description {
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .see-also {
      background: var(--surface);
      padding: var(--space-6);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    }

    .see-also-list {
      list-style: none;
      margin-top: var(--space-4);
    }

    .see-also-list li {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
      background: var(--brand);
      color: var(--bg);
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: var(--surface);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-menu {
        display: none;
      }

      .hero-title {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .main {
        padding: var(--space-4);
      }

      .grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .integration-tabs {
        overflow-x: auto;
        flex-wrap: nowrap;
      }

      .hero-actions {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: stretch;
      }

      .step {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: var(--space-3);
      }
    }
  </style>
</body>
</html>